<h2><br/>
Experiments with Social Network Interventions – Nicholas A. Christakis</h2>
<p> <iframe width="100" height="350" src="https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/WJ323v8Dfl0?version=3&amp;rel=1&amp;showsearch=0&amp;showinfo=1&amp;iv_load_policy=1&amp;fs=1&amp;hl=en&amp;autohide=2&amp;wmode=transparent" allowfullscreen="true" sandbox="allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups" loading="lazy"></iframe><br/>
